# 1️⃣ Print numbers from 1 to 100

```javascript
for(let i = 1; i <= 100; i++){
    console.log(i);
}
```

---

# 2️⃣ Print even numbers from 1 to 100

```javascript
for(let i = 1; i <= 100; i++){
    if(i % 2 === 0){
        console.log(i);
    }
}
```

---

# 3️⃣ Print odd numbers from 1 to 100

```javascript
for(let i = 1; i <= 100; i++){
    if(i % 2 !== 0){
        console.log(i);
    }
}
```

