# 7️⃣ Check prime number

```javascript
let num = prompt("Enter number");
let prime = true;

for(let i = 2; i < num; i++){
    if(num % i === 0){
        prime = false;
        break;
    }
}

if(prime){
    console.log("Prime number");
}
else{
    console.log("Not prime");
}
```

