# 1️⃣5️⃣ Remove duplicates from array

```javascript
let arr = [1,2,2,3,4,4,5];

let unique = [];

for(let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++){
    if(!unique.includes(arr[i])){
        unique.push(arr[i]);
    }
}

console.log(unique);
```

