# 1️⃣6️⃣ Count frequency of elements

```javascript
let arr = [1,2,2,3,3,3,4];

let freq = {};

for(let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++){
    if(freq[arr[i]]){
        freq[arr[i]]++;
    }
    else{
        freq[arr[i]] = 1;
    }
}

console.log(freq);
```

