# 1️⃣9️⃣ FizzBuzz (very famous interview question)

```javascript
for(let i = 1; i <= 100; i++){

    if(i % 3 === 0 && i % 5 === 0){
        console.log("FizzBuzz");
    }
    else if(i % 3 === 0){
        console.log("Fizz");
    }
    else if(i % 5 === 0){
        console.log("Buzz");
    }
    else{
        console.log(i);
    }
}
```

